454
00:31:42,673 --> 00:31:44,874
Sudah dimulai!
Cepat kesini!

455
00:31:49,173 --> 00:31:51,273
Tuan Soo Hyun, apa kamu baik-baik saja?

456
00:31:51,273 --> 00:31:53,074
Sejak kapan dia seperti ini?

457
00:31:53,074 --> 00:31:54,673
Segera setelah kamu pergi!

458
00:31:58,074 --> 00:32:00,473
Tuan Sung Oh! Tunggu!
Tuan Sung Oh!

459
00:32:01,598 --> 00:32:05,500
Tuan Sung Oh!

