00:33:03,115 --> 00:33:04,815
Alien!
Alien!

471
00:33:04,815 --> 00:33:06,414
- Berhenti disana!
- Berhenti disana!

472
00:33:06,414 --> 00:33:10,315
Tidak, bukan aku...
pria yang kabur...

