00:33:10,315 --> 00:33:12,213
Tuan!
Hei!

474
00:33:14,914 --> 00:33:17,713
Bukan aku!

475
00:33:17,713 --> 00:33:21,115
Tuan!
Ow!

476
00:33:27,815 --> 00:33:30,513
